      "title": "Ranil will be sworn in as President tomorrow",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ranil Wickramasinghe will be sworn in as the eighth executive president of the Socialist Republic of Sri Lanka tomorrow, Thursday (21) morning.",
        "It is noteworthy that Ranil Wickremesinghe had requested the Speaker today to allow him to take oath as President in the Parliament premises."
      ],
